entries.femaleVariant: Say, you ever rub shoulders with FIA folks? Just so happens yours truly got a covert mission from 'em, got it done…
Did some work for the FIA recently.
Heh, not all that covert if you're spillin' it all to me. For real, though?
Took a trip to Dogtown.
Saved the life of the president of the NUSA.
Took a trip to Dogtown. Technically? Could say I went abroad.
You hear about Space Force One? How it crashed in Dogtown?
Mhm. Tracked a murderer once who holed up there.
Was on every screen – how could I not hear? Why do you ask?
Got an in with MaxTac, know anyone?
Got a favor to ask - kind you're probably-- no, definitely not gonna like, but... well, could use your help.
Listen, River, don't want this to sound like I'm cashin' in a favor or anythin', but... could really use your help.
Can't say I like where this is headin'... But OK – hit me.
Need info on a MaxTac convoy –  itinerary, vehicle array, fear they'lll be packin'... They'll be transportin' someone I know, so--
Stop, V, are you insane? We drop this subject now – make like this convo never happened.
Look, V, I know I owe you – big time. But I can't access that kind of data. And even if I could, there're some lines I'm just not willin' to cross. I'm sorry.
Don't sweat it, V. What's on your mind?
Need info on a MaxTac convoy. It'll be en route to Los Padres via Dogtown. Itinerary, vehicle array, gear they'll be packin' – any intel you could pull…
V... sorry, but you're askin' for the impossible. Even if I was still on the force, MaxTac records are classified, need-to-know only.
Well, I get it. Was worth a shot, though. I'll keep lookin'.
Not like this convo ever took place, but... watch out for yourself, V, OK? Don't mess with those guys. The prey they hunt, well... sometimes there's not a whole lot separatin' 'em.
They have their own dataforts – not linked to any police precincts. And then everything's guarded by that AI of theirs, uh, Harriet. So it's a no, V. Sorry.
Appreciate the heads up, River. Thanks.
River, wouldn't be askin' if it wasn't really damn important.
Got nothin' to apologize for, River. Like you said, convo never happened.
FIA might cure me, save my life.
Tell you about it over a beer?
Turns out FIA might be able to treat my, uh... affliction. Got a real shot at survival, River.
They put that in writing? A contract, signed and sealed, all promises initialed?
Tell you more over a cold one sometime.
Media didn't dish the full scoop. Choom who saved the president's life? Yours truly.
Rosalind Myers? You rescued President Myers after that crash?
First a Night City mayor-in-the-running, now the NUSA president... Could say you're dippin' your hand into politics.
You're thinkin' they took advantage of a desperate soul – that as soon it's over it'll be "Whoops, sorry, can't help ya."
I didn't say that. Sure as hell hope not. Just don't get fucked – that's all I'm sayin'. And if you need help, you know where to find me.
Really? You find him?
Nah, locals beat me to him. Guy pissed off some of Hansen's goons, who promptly zeroed him. Me? Hm, asked too many questions, barely got out alive. I'll fill in the blanks for you sometime.
Oh, you'd better.
